Product description

India Gate Basmati Rice Everyday originates from the heart of the basmati-growing land of India - the North-Western Himalayan region. The highest quality harvest of the region is tested, procured, and then sent for aging in the most conducive environment of the company-owned storage facilities. India Gate Basmati Rice Everyday has a burst of flavor to savor your taste buds combined with a aroma that's so delicate that makes your regular dishes irresistible.
